headline: Salient Motion to Showcase Commercial and Military Actuation Systems with Boeing Ventures at Dubai Airshow 2025
summary: TORRANCE, Calif. & DUBAI, United Arab Emirates, November 11, 2025--(Dubai Airshow)—Salient Motion, an aerospace and defense component supplier, will showcase its modular actuation systems and motion control technologies at Dubai Airshow 2025, running Nov. 17-21.
